
INSTALL

  To install:
  $ make
  $ sudo make install

  or specify the installation directory:
  $ sudo make install DESTDIR=/opt


SUDOERS

  Add a line with your user or group in sudoers(8):
  <user_or_group>  ALL=(ALL) NOPASSWD: /usr/share/safe-crux/scx


PACKAGES

  To create a CRUX package:
  $ pkgmk

  or better:
  $ fakeroot pkgmk
